lines.text: i've told myself so many times before
but this time i think i mean it for sure
we have reached a full stop
nothing's going to save us from the big drop
i hate being in these situations
if i only knew the answer
or i thought we had a chance
i don't want to play any more
i can't stand this emotional violence
we've been running round in circles all year
doing this and that and getting nowhere
this will be the last time
i think i said the last- time
if i only had a potion
i would stop this, i would set-the wheels in motion
i don't want to play any more
i can't stand this emotional violence
